{"tid":728701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[同志又贏一仗]女同志申請受養人簽證案 入境處終極敗訴","createTime":"2018-07-04T02:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T22:20:43.000Z","uid":59328,"like":18,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1b72c898333788228e5dbc4cfb1f1bb3dbb8e1","tid":728701,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:48:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%8F%97%E9%A4%8A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E7%B5%82%E6%A5%B5%E6%95%97%E8%A8%B4-023036953.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BF%2597%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%258F%2597%25E9%25A4%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%25A1%2588%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2599%2595%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2595%2597%25E8%25A8%25B4-023036953.html&d=Eb0W3O0KtXZ08nsU8PCOagRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e5e64511\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%B3%E5%90%8C%E5%BF%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%8F%97%E9%A4%8A%E4%BA%BA%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89%E6%A1%88%E3%80%80%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%99%95%E7%B5%82%E6%A5%B5%E6%95%97%E8%A8%B4-023036953.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英籍女同性戀者申請以伴侶身份來港案，終審法院今日頒下判詞，駁回入境處上訴。<br />\n<br />\n案中事主QT與伴侶在英國註冊結合後，其伴侶來港工作，QT申請以受養人身份留港，遭入境處拒絕。<br />\n<br />\nQT不服提出司法覆核，於原訟庭被判敗訴，上訴庭改判其上訴得直，指入境處做法構成性傾向歧視。入境處上月於終審法院提出終極上訴，終院5位法官一致裁定，駁回入境處的上訴。"},{"pid":"1aa8db4d7a512b2421300457474cf5389c66d226","tid":728701,"uid":34410,"like":17,"dislike":18,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"香港唔承認同性婚姻法庭要被迫政府接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次一夫多妻黎香港申請4-5個老婆黎咪都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係又係同性戀大哂"},{"pid":"07884eeff4d459da8ed27a4a48075e65b170c670","tid":728701,"uid":30202,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-